actions.message:
The following rules are to be followed at all times while within this Discord server. Violation of any of these rules will result in a punishment depending on the severity.

**1. No spam of any sort.**
This includes abusing mentions, mic spam or spamming any channel.

**2. No excessive swearing.**
This group is based around a Roblox group, while swearing is fine, keep it within its limitations.

**3. No disrespect towards other members of the community.**
This is not the place for it, if it comes to it, take to to DMs.

**4. No offensive/derogitory terms.**
This is a place for everyone, no offensive terms are allowed.

**5. No advertising or posting of unrelated discords.**
Keep everything related to this USA group.

**6. No personal information of yourself or anyone else.**
We do not need people getting into arguments over getting themselves shown, whether done intentionally or not, do not post it.

**7. No abusing channels, use them for their intended purposes.**
No general discussion in any sort of announcement channel.

**8. Do not abuse mentions.**
Mentions in announcements will be kept for only important information. We don't care that Donald Trump opened a book the wrong way.

**9. Do not attempt to find loopholes around any rules.**
Of course we did not label everything, if you attempt to void any rules through any sort of loopholes, you will be banned.

This server is property of sagesoup and is subject to rule change at any time. While we do belive in the concept of freedom of speech, certain things that shall not be discussed will be removed.
